<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff">
<title>Pascua Juvenil 2026 · Primer Sagrario</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --orange:#f5a623;--orange-dark:#e8870a;--yellow:#f9c22e;
  --teal:#2177a0;--teal-light:#2a9acc;--purple:#3d2060;
  --blue-ps:#1a4fa0;--bg:#fff;--surface:#f7f7f5;--surface2:#eeecea;
  --border:#e2ddd6;--text:#1a1a1a;--text2:#555;--text3:#888;
  --radius:16px;--radius-sm:10px;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;}
html,body{background:#fff;color:var(--text);font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;}
.cintillo-img{width:100%; display:block; height:32px; object-fit:cover; object-position:top;}
.view{display:none;min-height:100vh;flex-direction:column;background:#fff;}
.view.active{display:flex;}
/* SPLASH */
.splash-body{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;padding:1rem 1.25rem 0.75rem;justify-content:center;}
.pascua-logo-wrap{width:100%;max-width:200px;margin-bottom:0.75rem;}
.pascua-logo-wrap img{width:100%;height:auto;display:block;}
.bottom-logos{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;width:100%;max-width:300px;}
.bottom-logos img.logo-ps{height:60px;width:auto;}
.bottom-logos img.logo-cv{height:48px;width:auto;}
.logos-divider{width:1px;height:44px;background:var(--border);flex-shrink:0;}
.splash-invite-main{font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);line-height:1.3;}
.splash-invite-sub{font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text2);}
.moment-cards{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.85rem;width:100%;max-width:360px;}
.moment-card{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.15rem 1.2rem;cursor:pointer;transition:transform 0.13s,box-shadow 0.13s;text-align:left;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.85rem;border:2px solid var(--border);box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);}
.moment-card:active{transform:scale(0.97);}
.moment-card.adoracion{border-color:var(--teal);}
.moment-card.misa{border-color:var(--orange);}
.moment-icon{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.ic-adoracion{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--teal),var(--teal-light));}
.ic-misa{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--orange-dark),var(--yellow));}
.moment-icon svg{width:26px;height:26px;}
.moment-info{flex:1;}
.moment-name{font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:0.15rem;line-height:1.2;}
.moment-count{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--text3);font-weight:600;}
.moment-arrow{font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:900;}
.moment-card.adoracion .moment-arrow{color:var(--teal);}
.moment-card.misa .moment-arrow{color:var(--orange);}
.splash-footer{padding:1rem 1rem 0.75rem;text-align:center;font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--text3);font-weight:700;border-top:1px solid var(--border);letter-spacing:0.03em;line-height:1.6;}
/* LIST */
.list-header{background:#fff;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);}
.list-header-main{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;padding:0.85rem 1rem 0.75rem;}
.back-btn{background:var(--surface);border:1.5px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);cursor:pointer;padding:5px 11px;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;}
.list-title-wrap{flex:1;min-width:0;}
.list-title{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);line-height:1.2;}
.list-subtitle{font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--text3);font-weight:600;}
.list-header-logo{height:36px;width:auto;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;}
.progress-wrap{padding:0 1rem 0.75rem;}
.progress-bar{height:6px;background:var(--surface2);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;}
.progress-fill{height:100%;border-radius:6px;transition:width 0.4s;width:0%;}
.pf-adoracion{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--teal),var(--teal-light));}
.pf-misa{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--orange-dark),var(--yellow));}
.progress-label{font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text3);text-align:right;margin-top:3px;}
.songs-container{flex:1;padding:0.25rem 0 5rem;}
.song-item{display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0.85rem 1rem;gap:0.85rem;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:background 0.1s;background:#fff;}
.song-item:active{background:var(--surface);}
.song-item.done{background:#f5fdf7;}
.song-num{font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--border);width:20px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.song-item.done .song-num{color:var(--orange);}
.song-info{flex:1;min-width:0;}
.song-title-sm{font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;}
.song-artist-sm{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--text3);font-style:italic;font-weight:600;}
.song-badge{font-size:0.58rem;padding:3px 7px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.04em;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;text-transform:uppercase;}
.badge-adoracion{background:rgba(33,119,160,0.1);color:var(--teal);}
.badge-misa{background:rgba(245,166,35,0.12);color:var(--orange-dark);}
.song-check{width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all 0.2s;font-size:11px;font-weight:900;color:transparent;}
.song-item.done .song-check{background:var(--orange);border-color:var(--orange);color:#fff;}
/* SONG VIEW */
#song-view{background:#fff;}
.song-header{background:#fff;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);}
.song-header-main{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;padding:0.85rem 1rem 0.5rem;}
.song-meta{flex:1;min-width:0;}
.song-badge-view{display:inline-block;font-size:0.58rem;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.3rem;}
.song-title-lg{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);line-height:1.25;}
.song-artist-tag{font-size:0.73rem;color:var(--text3);font-style:italic;font-weight:600;margin-top:0.1rem;display:block;}
.song-nav{display:flex;gap:0.5rem;align-items:center;padding:0 1rem 0.75rem;}
.nav-btn{background:var(--surface);border:1.5px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);cursor:pointer;padding:7px 14px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:0.82rem;font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;font-weight:700;transition:all 0.13s;flex:1;text-align:center;}
.nav-btn:active{transform:scale(0.97);}
.nav-btn:disabled{opacity:0.3;cursor:not-allowed;}
.next-adoracion{background:rgba(33,119,160,0.08);border-color:var(--teal);color:var(--teal);}
.next-misa{background:rgba(245,166,35,0.1);border-color:var(--orange);color:var(--orange-dark);}
.song-counter{font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;min-width:44px;}
/* LYRICS */
.lyrics-body{padding:1.5rem 1.25rem 7rem;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.9;color:var(--text);overflow-y:auto;height:calc(100vh - 160px);}
.lyric-section{margin-bottom:1.4rem;}
.lyric-section-label{font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.4rem;display:block;}
.lsl-misa{color:var(--orange-dark);}.lsl-adoracion{color:var(--teal);}
.lyric-line{display:block;margin-bottom:0.05rem;}
.lyric-line.bold{font-weight:800;}
.lyric-line.italic{font-style:italic;color:var(--text2);}
.lyric-sep{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;margin:1.2rem 0;}
.lyric-sep::before,.lyric-sep::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1.5px;background:var(--border);border-radius:2px;}
.lyric-sep-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;}
.dot-misa{background:var(--yellow);}.dot-adoracion{background:var(--teal-light);}
.note-box{border-radius:0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;padding:0.6rem 0.9rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem;font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:700;font-style:italic;}
.note-misa{background:rgba(245,166,35,0.08);border-left:3px solid var(--orange);color:var(--orange-dark);}
.note-adoracion{background:rgba(33,119,160,0.07);border-left:3px solid var(--teal);color:var(--teal);}
.bilingual-block{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:0.75rem;background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.8;border:1px solid var(--border);}
.lang-label{font-size:0.58rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(--text3);text-transform:uppercase;display:block;margin-bottom:0.35rem;}
/* READ PROGRESS */
.read-progress-bar{position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:4px;background:var(--surface2);z-index:30;}
.read-progress-fill{height:100%;width:0%;transition:width 0.15s;}
.rpf-misa{background:var(--orange);}.rpf-adoracion{background:var(--teal);}
/* MARK CTA */
.mark-cta{position:fixed;bottom:1rem;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);z-index:20;display:none;}
.mark-cta.visible{display:block;}
.mark-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;padding:0.75rem 1.5rem;border-radius:40px;border:none;font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:800;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 4px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);transition:all 0.15s;white-space:nowrap;letter-spacing:0.02em;}
.mark-btn:active{transform:scale(0.96);}
.mb-misa{background:var(--orange);color:#fff;}
.mb-adoracion{background:var(--teal);color:#fff;}
.mb-done{background:var(--surface2);color:var(--text3);box-shadow:none;}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- SPLASH -->
<div class="view active" id="splash">
<img class="cintillo-img" src="images/Cintillo.png" alt="">
  <div class="splash-body">
    <div class="pascua-logo-wrap">
      <img src="images/PascuaJuvenil.png">
    </div>
    <div class="bottom-logos">
      <img src="images/PrimerSagrario.jpg">
      <div class="logos-divider"></div>
      <img src="CristoViveynosLlama.png">
    </div>
    <div class="splash-invite">
      <p class="splash-invite-main">Acompáñanos en la celebración</p>
      <p class="splash-invite-sub">siguiendo los cantos del repertorio</p>
    </div>
    <div class="moment-cards">
      <div class="moment-card adoracion" onclick="openSection('adoracion')">
        <div class="moment-icon ic-adoracion">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
            <path d="M12 3l1.5 4.5H18l-3.75 2.7 1.5 4.5L12 12.5l-3.75 2.2 1.5-4.5L6 7.5h4.5z"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="20" r="1.5" fill="white" stroke="none"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="moment-info">
          <p class="moment-name">Adoración Eucarística</p>
          <p class="moment-count">10 cantos · Santísimo</p>
        </div>
        <span class="moment-arrow">›</span>
      </div>
      <div class="moment-card misa" onclick="openSection('misa')">
        <div class="moment-icon ic-misa">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
            <path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2.5" fill="white" stroke="none"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="moment-info">
          <p class="moment-name">Santa Misa</p>
          <p class="moment-count">11 cantos · Hora Santa</p>
        </div>
        <span class="moment-arrow">›</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- CINTILLO INFERIOR -->
  <img class="cintillo-img" src="images/Cintillo.png" alt="">
  <div class="splash-footer">
    Coro Juvenil Primer Sagrario · Pastoral Juvenil<br>
    Catedral Metropolitana · Decanato 1 · Guatemala 2026 · @catedral.metropolitana
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SONG LIST -->
<div class="view" id="song-list">
  <div class="list-header">
    <img class="cintillo-img" src="images/Cintillo.png" alt="">
    <div class="list-header-main">
      <button class="back-btn" onclick="goHome()">‹</button>
      <div class="list-title-wrap">
        <p class="list-title" id="list-title"></p>
        <p class="list-subtitle" id="list-subtitle"></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="progress-wrap">
    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progress-fill"></div></div>
    <p class="progress-label" id="progress-label"></p>
  </div>
  <div class="songs-container" id="songs-container"></div>
</div>

<!-- SONG VIEW -->
<div class="view" id="song-view">
  <div class="song-header">
    <img class="cintillo-img" src="images/Cintillo.png" alt="">
    <div class="song-header-main">
      <button class="back-btn" onclick="goList()">‹</button>
      <div class="song-meta">
        <span class="song-badge-view" id="view-badge"></span>
        <p class="song-title-lg" id="view-title"></p>
        <span class="song-artist-tag" id="view-artist"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="song-nav">
      <button class="nav-btn" id="prev-btn" onclick="prevSong()">‹ Anterior</button>
      <span class="song-counter" id="song-counter"></span>
      <button class="nav-btn" id="next-btn" onclick="nextSong()">Siguiente ›</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="lyrics-body" id="lyrics-body" onscroll="onLyricsScroll()"></div>
  <div class="read-progress-bar"><div class="read-progress-fill" id="read-progress-fill"></div></div>
</div>

<!-- MARK CTA -->
<div class="mark-cta" id="mark-cta">
  <button class="mark-btn" id="mark-btn" onclick="toggleDone()">
    <span id="mark-btn-icon">♪</span>
    <span id="mark-btn-label">Marcar como cantado</span>
  </button>
</div>

<script>
const SONGS = {
  adoracion: [
    {title:"Cantemos al Amor de los amores",artist:"Himno Eucarístico",badge:"Exposición",lyrics:`<div class="note-box note-adoracion">✦ Exposición del Santísimo</div><div class="lyric-section"><span class="lyric-line">Cantemos al amor de los amores,</span><span class="lyric-line">cantemos al Señor,</span><span class="lyric-line">Dios está aquí, venid adoradores adoremos</span><span class="lyric-line">a Cristo Redentor.</span></div><div class="lyric-sep"><div class="lyric-sep-dot dot-adoracion"></div></div><div class="lyric-section"><span class="lyric-section-label lsl-adoracion">Estribillo</span><span class="lyric-line bold">Gloria a Cristo Jesús,</span><span class="lyric-line bold">cielos y tierra bendecid al Señor;</span><span class="lyric-line bold">honor y gloria a Ti,</span><span class="lyric-line bold">Rey de la gloria, amor por siempre a Ti,</span><span class="lyric-line bold">Dios del amor.</span></div><div class="lyric-sep"><div class="lyric-sep-dot dot-adoracion"></div></div><div class="lyric-section"><span class="lyric-line">Unamos nuestra voz a los cantares</span><span class="lyric-line">del coro celestial;</span><span class="lyric-line">Dios está aquí;</span><span class="lyric-line">al Dios de los altares alabemos</span><span class="lyric-line">con gozo angelical.</span></div>`},
    {title:"Alabemos al Santísimo",artist:"Canto Tradicional",badge:"Adoración",lyrics:`<div class="lyric-section"><span class="lyric-section-label lsl-adoracion">Estribillo</span><span class="lyric-line bold">Alabemos al Santísimo</span><span class="lyric-line bold">Sacramento del altar,</span><span class="lyric-line bold">y a María, concebida</span><span class="lyric-line bold">sin pecado original.</span></div><div class="lyric-sep"><div class="lyric-sep-dot dot-adoracion"></div></div><div class="lyric-section"><span class="lyric-section-label lsl-adoracion">1</span><span class="lyric-line">Vuestro cuerpo sacrosanto</span><span class="lyric-line">benignísimo Señor,</span><span class="lyric-line">prenda sea que nos una</span><span class="lyric-line">hasta la eternidad.</span></div><div class="lyric-sep"><div class="lyric-sep-dot dot-adoracion"></div></div><div class="lyric-section"><span class="lyric-section-label lsl-adoracion">2</span><span class="lyric-line">Vuestro cuerpo sacrosanto</span><span class="lyric-line">es del cielo rico don;</span><span class="lyric-line">es de fuertes: alimento;</span><span class="lyric-line">es de débiles: vigor.</span></div><div class="lyric-sep"><div class="lyric-sep-dot dot-adoracion"></div></div><div class="lyric-section"><span class="lyric-section-label lsl-adoracion">3</span><span class="lyric-line">Oh cristianos que dulzura</span><span class="lyric-line">halla el alma en visitar</span><span class="lyric-line">a Jesús que con ternura</span><span class="lyric-line">nos da audiencia en el altar.</span></div>`},
    {title:"Tan cerca de mí",artist:"Luis Alfredo Díaz",badge:"Adoración",lyrics:`<div class="lyric-section"><span class="lyric-section-label lsl-adoracion">Estribillo</span><span class="lyric-line bold">Tan cerca de mí,</span><span class="lyric-line bold">tan cerca de mí,</span><span class="lyric-line bold">que hasta lo puedo tocar,</span><span class="lyric-line bold">Jesús está aquí.</span></div><div class="lyric-sep"><div class="lyric-sep-dot dot-adoracion"></div></div><div class="lyric-section"><span class="lyric-line">Le hablaré sin miedo al oído,</span><span class="lyric-line">le contaré las cosas que hay en mí;</span><span class="lyric-line">y que solo a Él le interesarán,</span><span class="lyric-line">Él es más que un mito para mí…</span><span class="lyric-line italic">Tan cerca de ti…</span></div><div class="lyric-sep"><div class="lyric-sep-dot dot-adoracion"></div></div><div class="lyric-section"><span class="lyric-line">No busques a Cristo en lo alto,</span><span class="lyric-line">ni lo busques en la oscuridad;</span><span class="lyric-line">muy cerca de ti, en tu corazón,</span><span class="lyric-line">puedes adorar a tu Señor…</span><span class="lyric-line italic">Tan cerca de mí…</span></div><div class="lyric-sep"><div class="lyric-sep-dot dot-adoracion"></div></div><div class="lyric-section"><span class="lyric-line">Míralo a tu lado caminando,</span><span class="lyric-line">paseando entre la multitud;</span><span class="lyric-line">muchos ciegos son, porque no lo ven,</span><span class="lyric-line">ciegos de ceguera espiritual…</span><span class="lyric-line italic">Tan cerca de mí…</span></div>`},
